title: MAGBLOCK Magnetic Stylus Drawing Board with Magnat Pen, Educational Read Write Learn Preschool Gift for Boys and Girls (12.4in x 10in)

Magnet Tablet Pad as a gift for a toddler that is going to pre-school soon.
